window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The first second of a quiet living, slice-of-life LitRPG about farming.</b></p> <p><b>A year has passed in the town of Summer Shandy.</b></p> <p>The farmstead outside of town isn't quite as run-down as it used to be. The fields still need to be tended, the monsters still need to be handled, and the soil will always need a tilling. That's life. And for Jason Hunter, it's a good one. At least it would be if it wasn't for those out-of-towners.</p> <p><b>Get a copy of this farming coziness and embark on a quiet adventure!</b></p>"; 
